window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>Shane &amp; Michelle</i></b><b> is the fateful ending of the Trust Not Thy Neighbor: Who Is My Neighbor? series.</b></p> <p>This book reveals vital, unpublished events that took place in the lives of the characters that are unknown to the listeners. This book picks up where the <i>Within the Shadows</i> book in the series left off and takes you to an exciting, yet heartfelt, fateful conclusion. </p> <p><i>Shane &amp; Michelle</i> meets the long-awaited expectations and hopes of certain listeners who were held in suspense as one of the main characters themselves. Even though the book is entitled <i>Shane &amp; Michelle</i>, it gives justifiable closure to a lot that transpires over the series, thus giving a fateful ending to the entire series in <i>Shane &amp; Michelle</i>.</p>"; 
